adds native gamma support for 3dfx Voodoo1/2 to tyrquake-0.55 and 0.56
on linux through some glide hacks which are self-contained in the newly
created fx_gamma.c. it is a compile time makefile option.

also allows voodoo1/2 to be detected and in that case set VID_SetGammaRamp
to NULL and made VID_IsFullscreen to return false.

tyrquake homepage is at: http://disenchant.net/


